Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.47,0:00:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飘忽不定的罪孽之影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.22,0:00:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可悲的宿命 迷失的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.69,0:00:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因憎恨和被憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而破碎的两面镜子 是双重的枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.81,0:00:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在交错的时光与黑暗中浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的怨恨  替你消除
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一个被人叫做恶魔之子的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.85,0:01:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他周围的人陆续消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.58,0:01:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他明明什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实只是市民用地狱通信消除怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们想把失踪事件全部归罪于红林拓真
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 阴谋不会如此轻易得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年轻的警察觉察到了他们的诡计
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.37,0:02:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个警察串通恶魔之子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要让我们消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后警察救出了被他们拘禁险些丧命的拓真和妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果就此真相大白  一切就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本该如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 哥哥 哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0054,,警察被流放了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,染蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了 拓真
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我别无选择
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.44,0:03:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只能这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能让你消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我不会让你孤单一人的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.31,0:03:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也马上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要他在 这一切就无法结束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他的错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要他不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨的连锁就会终止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会终止的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请把草人给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一目连
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗 小姐 那个孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你若真的要消除怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不说我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.97,0:05:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也会下地狱对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就跟过去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨已闻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃糖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怜啊 明明什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事以前也发生过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拓真
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一想到小姐的心情 就让人受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这或许就是命运吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此 也太残酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子现在已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他没有下地狱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菊理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有下地狱是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 该不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.04,0:07:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱把船又划回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船回去了 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.32,0:08:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 放开我 秃瓢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐在哪儿 她到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都说了我不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快说 菊理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.19,0:09:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地狱里的大人 小姐怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱让红林拓真回到了现世
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然没有遵守规则
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱和她所爱之人的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将永远在黑暗中不得超生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只救了他一个人不算什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐四百年来一直兢兢业业
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她舍弃自我 连那些不合理的怨恨都一一回应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是多么漫长 多么痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.21,0:10:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是小姐一直很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.34,0:10:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底要消除多少怨恨 才可以让小姐获得解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.91,0:10:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让她解脱吧 已经够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女的任务已结束
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱已经返回现世
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐可以解脱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,错 不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 不是那回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轮入道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在小姐回到人间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐体内四百年的岁月就会一下子爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.33,0:11:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一目连
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去看着爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.57,0:11:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滑下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察才消失不久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们应该不会走远
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们找这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们去前边看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.06,0:11:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没结束吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经忍了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸总是跟我说 不可以怨恨别人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经忍无可忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拓真
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拓真出现了 在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 追的时候别被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.98,0:13:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他好像冲着自己家这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.17,0:13:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们这就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公 你在干吗呢 给我适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消不掉  这印记消不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.53,0:13:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是弱不禁风
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.62,0:14:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 这么虚弱还…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,0:14:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请让开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 请让我过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事 轮入道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐已经不认识我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:14:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不认识是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 简直像失忆了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.15,0:15:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是传给我们的地狱的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,线被割断了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后我们就只能看着她了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拓真
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想烧了我家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.44,0:15:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.44,0:15:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:16:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道 你知道这么做的后果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 会下地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果真是恶魔之子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们为了自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们全都是恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拓真
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.15,0:16:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是我们不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.76,0:16:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们什么都不会做的 我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把打火机熄了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.76,0:16:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 早该把你杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.23,0:16:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁呼唤你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要让我们中间的谁下地狱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.49,0:17:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不能杀这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清醒清醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混帐 好好看着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阎魔爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.98,0:17:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来 一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要下地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在的小姐好像要给出答案了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.49,0:19:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.31,0:19:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 醒醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这么残忍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:19:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.45,0:20:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结束了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是爱所选择的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.84,0:21:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后 那位警察将对话录音向媒体公开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.32,0:21:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,红林拓真的冤屈被公证了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.60,0:21:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要嫁祸给那孩子的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻逃离镇子 不知所踪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然也没有对地狱通信的正面报道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在新兴住宅城区发生的集体疯狂事件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:21:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.32,0:22:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么煞风景啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.88,0:22:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这么等着 小姐也不会回来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.09,0:22:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱说要谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.16,0:22:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.87,0:22:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.56,0:22:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不像她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.73,0:22:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不像
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.64,0:23:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也来周游尘世 打扮一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.42,0:23:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说是周游地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.84,0:23:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.11,0:23:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝贺你出院
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 拓真
